| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0031 — Recovery Inhibition (agelocker)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 18849ee0-c2f5-52ab-940d-7b4b91c2b817"
